comment: Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on Wiggins (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Parker (SAS) makes marginal contact with Towns (MIN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt or ability to land.
Dieng (MIN) makes contact to Parker's (SAS) body that affects his SQBR.
Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on Wiggins (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gasol (SAS) and Dieng (MIN) briefly engage with one another during rebounding.
Dieng (MIN) makes marginal contact with Gasol (SAS) after the rebound.
Towns (MIN) makes contact with the ball and any contact with Gasol (SAS) is incidental. Towns does not make contact with Gasol's face.
Dunn (MIN) makes contact with the ball but also with Gasol's (SAS) arm and the contact affects his ability to make the pass.
Towns (MIN) makes contact with Leonard (SAS) that affects his SQBR.
Dieng (MIN) sets the screen on Ginobili (SAS) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Leonard (SAS) makes marginal contact with Rubio (MIN) and does not extend his arms into him.
[Observable in enhanced video] Rubio (MIN) and Towns (MIN) get their hands on the ball prior to the timeout awarded to SAS.
Rubio (MIN) commits a take foul on Ginobili (SAS).
